entries.title_d: This Veteran TIE commander has been a problem for too long. Your orders are to eliminate this threat to the Alliance. When you complete this mission, return to V3-FX in Moenia and V3-FX will train you in a new Rebel Alliance Pilot Skill.
entries.title: Naboo system: Hunt down the Imperial Veteran.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < It looks like the TIE Veteran had a malfunction and you will get another shot at him pilot. Don't mess up this time! >
entries.quest_target_d: Your target is in sight. Intercept and destroy it!
entries.quest_location_d: The Naboo system is crawling with the Imperial scum, be careful out there.
entries.failed_escape: You let him get away pilot! Return to base immediately.
entries.escort_wiped_out: Tactical Computer: < Scans show target vessel escort terminated. No more escort vessels remain. >
entries.escort_remaining: Tactical Computer: < Scans show target vessel escort terminated. %DI escort vessels remain. >
entries.assassinate_success: Excellent work pilot! The Empire won't underestimate the Alliance again. Return to base pilot.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Found him. Proceed to these coordinates and terminate him. We will update your coordinates as he's moving.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Stand by while we track down the TIE Veteran.
